<P>
The Russian ministry expressed its "concern that the process of
the Kosovo militants' disarmament is moving too slowly."
</P>
<P>
There is every ground to believe, the statement said, that "the
bulk of the arms to be laid down by the 60th day (August 20) of
demilitarization (of the Kosovo Liberation Army) will be
concealed."
</P>
<P>
The ministry warned of the risk that "the agreement on the
total disarmament of the Albanian extremists in Kosovo within 90
days will remain on paper as well." 
