that any body interested in getting the books and publications
listed for donation in the website can directly contact the donors
directly.
</P>
<P>
They can also contact any State Public Library which acts as
the central point linking both contributors and readers, she said.
</P>
<P>
The introduction of computers in libraries is vital to ensure
that rural folks are exposed to information technology, she said.
</P>
<P>
She said that even with the existence of the Internet, books
were still the main menu in any library. 
