followers have seen the true face of Li Hongzhi after the ban on
Falun Gong. The starting point of the ban on Falun Gong is to
safeguard the stability of the society, which is the paramount
interest of the State and the people. Continuous efforts are
needed to carry the struggle against the illegal Falun Gong cult
through to the end, in a bid to create a good environment for the
reform and opening-up.
</P>
