the reform of economic mechanisms is heading for a breakthrough.
Under such circumstances, Yunnan and other provinces and
autonomous regions must fully tap their potentials and develop
local economies with their own characteristics," Zhu said during
his August 12-16 inspection tour in Yunnan Province.
</P>
